{"tid":1065030,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA落實2021年搞24強球會世界盃","createTime":"2019-03-17T03:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T08:01:57.000Z","uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"59e43ddd3d4d900fc17266d0a3df2ea7de5577f5","tid":1065030,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"現時的世冠盃由來自6大洲的7支球隊參賽，但新的賽事將會每4年舉辦一次，由24支球隊角逐。<br />\n<br />\n雖然FIFA對新賽事讚不絕口，並指這是為配合世界足球發展而設，但不少球隊及組織均表示反對，歐洲球會協會已表明旗下球隊不會參賽。<br />\n<br />\n而UEFA亦對新賽事對歐聯的影響甚表關注，但FIFA表示有信心兩大組織最終可達成協議。"},{"pid":"c3b7097fd788a2e5e3671efdf66566be6dbcab63","tid":1065030,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:43:34.000Z","msg":"歐洲球會屈晒機"},{"pid":"142efa8c6a6427dbb39e7a8653b95dd224d094ae","tid":1065030,"uid":54264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:48:42.000Z","msg":"亞洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc4491484699b4157942779526af703527ebc56","tid":1065030,"uid":72415,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:53:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a63083c536afdd011d0fbf653409787fb42274fa","tid":1065030,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:57:17.000Z","msg":"到時仲牙朗36美欺34"},{"pid":"6a25a36d79ca681a7ebbecc881e356189f7ec528","tid":1065030,"uid":37062,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:58:30.000Z","msg":"幾時搞番圖圖盃"},{"pid":"2dea6ddda8fba79577d5b2d528251cf007a36c63","tid":1065030,"uid":25834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:59:42.000Z","msg":"認授性低過聯賽盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639579b52962b654c01563cd14211aa2c103663b","tid":1065030,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:01:58.000Z","msg":"國冠盃加強版？"},{"pid":"fe99ec4f8966c6a25059ab7bda6a6ad13275a5f1","tid":1065030,"uid":99861,"like":2,"dislike"